Package: zippy
Version: 0.1.0
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: The Zeta Foundation <murphsicles@proton.me>
Homepage: https://z-lang.org
Description: Zeta compiler installer — install the Zeta programming language
 Zippy is the Zeta toolchain installer. One command, one click, zero friction.
 It downloads, installs, and configures the Zeta compiler (zetac) on your system.
 .
 Features:
  - One-command Zeta installation
  - Automatic PATH configuration
  - Version management (install, update, list, default)
  - Diagnostic tools (zippy doctor)
  - Clean uninstall (zippy uninstall)
  - Beautiful terminal UI matching the Zeta amber palette
